1.6.0.name: wordpress/report-broken-links
1.6.0.description: This plugin simply adds a button to Your site and let users report Your site broken links/problem and You can see them in WP dashboard. Description Box let You get site visitors name, email or anything You need plus description of what is the problem but if You don't need this feature simply You can disable It from setting page With shortcode provided You can use plugin fully customized :)
